        # Selection of the Project 
        Our journey as a team in this year's iGEM competition began in January. 
        To decide on a project as quickly as possible, we first did a lot of brainstorming and compiled all the ideas. 
        In the following meetings, we selected which ideas would be feasible. Three projects emerged, which we divided among ourselves and worked out further. 
        At the end of February, we were able to present the more mature ideas to our supervisors and received positve feedback for two of these project ideas. 
        The final decision was made on March 12, 2021, where we chose our project "Storagene" for this year's iGEM competition.

